OL,6,FThe NWSF is hoping that this campaign
OL,7,Fwill help them to reduce accidental
OL,8,Fdrowning fatalities in the UK by 50%
OL,9,Fby 2026, and reduce the risk to the
OL,10,Fhighest risk populations.
OL,12,FThe campaign comes as two teenage boys
OL,13,Fdied after getting into difficulty in
OL,14,Fthe River Tyne in Northumberland.
OL,16,FThe teenagers were reported to be in
OL,17,Ftrouble in the water at Ovingham at
OL,18,Fabout 3.30pm on Saturday 18 May.
OL,20,FEmergency services carried out a large
OL,21,Fscale search and found
