OL,3,CRenewed water safety appeal to public
OL,4,Cas accidental drownings spiked in 2023
OL,6,FIt urges that if you see someone in
OL,7,Fdifficulty in the water this summer,
OL,8,Fstay calm, stay on land and follow
OL,9,Fthis three-step rescue guide - Call,
OL,10,FTell, Throw:
OL,12,F Call 999 to get help immediately
OL,14,F Tell the struggling person to float
OL,15,Fon their back
OL,17,F Throw them something that floats
